'''[[Rimmer]]'s Alley''' was a street in the [[Low Town]] neighborhood of the [[Sulon/Legends|Sulonese]] [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Barons Hed]].

It was part of the side street of the city and led towards the hill of [[Barons Knoll]]. The shops, [[cantina/Legends|cantinas]] and taverns had their doors permanently open. It was crowded by street vendors, beggars, [[bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]], [[Information broker/Legends|informers]], [[prostitute/Legends|prostitutes]] with glowing makeup and customers of the cantinas. Lights, glowing signs, music and various odors polluted the ambience.<ref name="RA">''[[Dark Forces: Rebel Agent]]''</ref>

During his [[mission to Sulon]], [[Kyle Katarn]] traversed the alley, hand on [[blaster/Legends|blaster]], trying not to draw attention; he, and a [[Unidentified female thief (Sulon)|bounty hunter following him]] ended up to a residential area with widely spaced [[lamp/Legends|streetlamps]].<ref name="RA" />

